{"tid":2054721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉國謙：人大會議通過國安法時 掌聲比「總理政府工作報告」更熱烈","createTime":"2020-06-07T11:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T15:53:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":21,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"7fddef3ff8d8649012cb686045796c7621527c7a","tid":2054721,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"港區人大代表葉國謙表示，美國政府就港區國安法提出制裁本港官員是恐嚇，他不會害怕，亦顯示中央更有必要出手，立法堵塞國家安全漏洞，阻止外國勢力干預本港。葉國謙出席一個論壇時表示，香港出現恐怖主義，但現時未有相關法例，他舉例指黑衣人「私了」的行為，現時只能循人身侵犯或襲擊罪追究，不夠阻嚇力，相信港區國安法立法後，會嚴厲打擊相關恐怖主義，並會強化特區政府，就國家安全的執法機制和能力。<br />\n<br />\n葉國謙強調，市民可就立法提出意見，現時已收到300萬人網上聯署表態支持立法，<span style=\"color: red;\">又形容人大會議通過港區國安法決定草案時，掌聲比總理的政府工作報告更熱烈，相信不少人對立法是熱切期盼</span>。"},{"pid":"00b82e87f0c3213cff6f362d61177cd3dc9df9f6","tid":2054721,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:12:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1302490&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1302490%26csid%3D261_341&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=49afbdb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1302490&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2f3d4a05918df63deb10ed70b6a15c88254bdaf9","tid":2054721,"uid":18477,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"老懵董到連幻覺都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037b64df42c058c2b8199806f21bbbd985bbf1b6","tid":2054721,"uid":132587,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06